title: 10 Takeaways From Week 8, Leonard Williams trade analysis
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways From Week 8, Leonard Williams trade analysis
description:
Daniel Jeremiah, Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis are back to discuss the latest news after Week 8, including Leonard Williams getting traded to the Giants (0:30) & J.J. Watt out for the season (3:40). Then, the guys recap the biggest takeaways of Week 8: Drew Brees returning from his injury (5:25), Deshaun Watson is playing like an MVP (8:20), Cooper Kupp makes history in London (10:30), Chargers’ 1-point win over the Bears (14:10), 49ers are contenders (18:05), Minshew continues to make plays (21:45), Patriots take care of the Browns (24:25), Eagles run through the Bills (30:20), Colts continue to win (32:35), Aaron Jones was a star on Sunday Night (34:50).
